<div class="jumbotron">
  <%= display_name_admin_header(@user) %>
  <h2>All <%= @user.height %> inches of you are looking extra beefy today, hope you are enjoying the rides!</h2>
  <p>Looks like you are in a <%= @user.mood %> Mood! Tickets: <%= @user.tickets %></p>
  <!-- <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="<%= edit_user_url %>" role="button">Edit your profile</a> -->
  <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="<%= attractions_url %>" role="button">See attractions</a>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h2>Happiness</h2>
      <p>Wow our happiness meters are reading a value of <%= @user.happiness %> coming from your body.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h2>Tickets</h2>
      <p>You currently have <%= @user.tickets %> ticket(s).  Woohoo!</p>
   </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h2>Nausea</h2>
      <p>Not sure why we have these but our nausea meters are reading a value of <%= @user.nausea %> coming from your body.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr>
</div>